{"about_the_game":"A challenging trivia card game with a randomly dealt deck each run. Test your knowledge by answering multiple choice questions of varying difficulty, earn tokens and use abilities to maximise your chances of conquering the board.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Randomised trivia deck</h2>Each run is a new challenge, battle your way through each column and maximise your score by getting consecutive answers.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829590/extras/TD-Deckload.gif?t=1708337847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Earn tokens</h2>Answer questions of varying difficulty correct to earn tokens and clear columns, the more difficult the question, the more tokens you earn.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829590/extras/TD-Correct.gif?t=1708337847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Purchase abilities</h2>Purchase strategic abilities such as the 50/50, slow timer, 2x token.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829590/extras/TD-Ability.gif?t=1708337847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Avoid mistakes</h2>Answering incorrectly will penalise you by locking that column, forcing you to spend 5 tokens to unlock with the key ability.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829590/extras/TD-Incorrect.gif?t=1708337847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Win the game</h2>Complete all columns to win the game, and try to beat your high score.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829590/extras/TD-WinGame.gif?t=1708337847\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demo features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original soundtrack<br></li><li>500+ multiple choice questions<br></li><li>9 trivia categories<br></li><li>4 abilities<br></li><li>Token purchase system</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite